Detailed Description

Structure to access the status of interrupts belonging to a group.

Structure to access the status of interrupts belonging to a High or Low priority interrupt.

uint32_t esmGroupIntrStatus::grpIntrStatus

Contains status for interrupts from a group

Indicates which Event Groups have one or more interrupts pending. This register is bit oriented where bit 0 is for Event Group 0, bit 1 is for Event Group 1, etcâ€¦ (bit N is for Event Group N).
